# Implementation Plan: LinkedIn Shield SOC Demo

We will build a high-fidelity, premium mini SOC (Security Operations Center) demo application called **LinkedIn Shield**. It will simulate a LinkedIn environment, run simulated cyber attacks (Data Scraping, Brute Force, and Suspicious APIs), monitor requests in real-time, execute AI threat detection rules, trigger automated response controls, and show a live breach timeline replay.

To ensure maximum visual impact for your presentation, we will build a stunning, fully animated React SPA using **Vanilla CSS** (dark-mode glassmorphic theme) and **Framer Motion** for micro-animations.

